影片的原创配乐由丹尼·本斯和桑德·朱里亚斯创作。专辑收录了多位独立音乐人的歌曲，横跨不同年代<ref name=":2">{{cite web|last=Fogarty|first=Paul|date=2021-01-22|title=The White Tiger soundtrack: Explore the songs, music and score of Indian Netflix film|url=https://www.hitc.com/en-gb/2021/01/22/the-white-tiger-soundtrack-songs-music-score-netflix/|access-date=2021-01-25|website=HITC|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123185933/https://www.hitc.com/en-gb/2021/01/22/the-white-tiger-soundtrack-songs-music-score-netflix/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Music from The White Tiger|url=https://www.tunefind.com/movie/the-white-tiger-2021|access-date=2021-01-25|website=Tunefind|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126035413/https://www.tunefind.com/movie/the-white-tiger-2021|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《Akh Lar Gayee》和《O Murari Re》两首歌以[[蒙太奇|蒙太奇]]的形式，出现在开车的戏份中。宣传曲《Jungle Mantra》讲述了巴拉姆的经历，由印度说唱歌手{{tsl|en|Divine (rapper)|Divine}}与美国说唱歌手{{tsl|en|Vince Staples|文斯·斯台普斯}}、[[普沙·T|普沙·T]]和贾瓦迪斯塔（Jawadista）表演，2021年1月15日发行<ref>{{cite web|title=DIVINE collaborates with American rappers Vince Staples and Pusha T for new song, Jungle Mantra|url=https://www.indulgexpress.com/culture/music/2021/jan/16/divine-collaborates-with-american-rappers-vince-staples-and-pusha-t-for-new-song-jungle-mantra-30974.html|access-date=2021-01-25|website=indulgexpress|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126035415/https://www.indulgexpress.com/culture/music/2021/jan/16/divine-collaborates-with-american-rappers-vince-staples-and-pusha-t-for-new-song-jungle-mantra-30974.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

配乐颇具印度风情<ref name=":2"/>。《{{tsl|en|Republic World|共和世界}}》的阿努什卡·帕坦尼亚（Anushka Pathania）认为每一幕的背景音乐都完美传递了角色的情感，吸引观众注意<ref>{{cite web|last=World|first=Republic|title='The White Tiger' Review: Adarsh Gourav roars in this enthralling tale about servitude|url=https://www.republicworld.com/entertainment-news/web-series/the-white-tiger-review-adarsh-gouravan-roars-in-this-enthralling-tale-about-servitude.html|access-date=2021-01-25|website=Republic World|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125141713/https://www.republicworld.com/entertainment-news/web-series/the-white-tiger-review-adarsh-gouravan-roars-in-this-enthralling-tale-about-servitude.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[印度斯坦时报|印度斯坦时报]]》的罗汉·纳哈尔（Rohan Naahar）称赞专辑用“强劲的嘻哈音乐及狂热的能量推动影片的发展”<ref>{{cite web|date=2021-01-22|title=The White Tiger movie review: Priyanka Chopra gives best performance in years, Adarsh Gourav roars in new Netflix film|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/hollywood/the-white-tiger-movie-review-adarsh-gourav-roars-in-ramin-bahrani-s-angry-answer-to-slumdog-millionaire-101611217488620.html|access-date=2021-01-25|website=Hindustan Times|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124164903/https://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/hollywood/the-white-tiger-movie-review-adarsh-gourav-roars-in-ramin-bahrani-s-angry-answer-to-slumdog-millionaire-101611217488620.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
